<img src="/uploads/1/2/7/2/127232404/published/ware-cv-thank-you-copypic-1.jpg?1686752779" alt="Picture" style="width:602;max-width:100%" />
</a>
<div style="display:block;font-size:90%"></div>
</div></div>

